title: Fernhill E1/E3/E4 — the vine chain, prune and wind, the hot poker
story: fernhill
description: The greenhouse vine's forward state chain (seedling warms to
  flowering via the machine, prunes to fruiting and yields the locket);
  the custom verbs `prune` and `wind` (grammar + must-gates + authored
  refusals over the stdlib default); the furnace poker's troll-axe-class
  take-refusal while the boiler runs.
---

